sub_title: Junior Full Stack JavaScript Developer  // HTML | CSS | JavaScript | Bootstrap | Material-UI | HandlebarsJs | ReactJs | ExpressJs | NodeJs | MongoDB | Mongoose | Axios |Git
summary:
Hi, I'm Maria,  a MERN Stack JavaScript Developer and full-time learner!

I'm a recent graduate of Ironhack's full stack web development boot camp. I'm looking forward to start my career in tech. 

After being interested in the programming world for some time this year I've decided to change industries and start a new career. So I enrolled in Ironhack's Web Development boot camp, which has been an intense but rewarding experience.  I've learnt so much during the last few weeks and I can't wait to keep growing in this new field. This short weeks have changed the way I look at things and I'm now a more curious person. 

Tecnologies: HTML | CSS | JavaScript | Bootstrap | Material-UI | HandlebarsJs | ReactJs | ExpressJs | NodeJs | MongoDB | Mongoose | Axios |Git

On a personal level my hobbies include reading and traveling. I'm super excited to move to a new country and discover a new way of living.
Let’s keep it touch! Feel free to reach me via direct message or at mariafarrancolell@gmail.com
